"content": "<h2>The destination of the righteous after death</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:43\">LUK 23:43</a></strong> <em>This Persian term originally described a park or pleasure garden. It was used by the Jews of the Garden of Eden, and of the future blessedness of the saints.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:3-2Cor12:4\">2CO 12:3–12:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a></p>",
